omas and venezuela the north latin america division nolad consisting of costa rica mexico and panama and the south latin america division slad consisting of argentina chile ecuador peru and uruguaythe companys brazil division operates approximately  restaurants its operations in brazil are based in sao paulo the caribbean division includes over  territories with approximately  restaurants the nolad division includes over three countries with approximately  restaurants the slad division includes over five countries with approximately  restaurants the company operates its mcdonaldsbranded restaurants under approximately two basic structures including companyoperated restaurants operated by the company and franchised restaurants operated by franchisees the company classifies its restaurants into one of four categories freestanding food court instore and mall stores the company has approximately  mccafe locations in the territories in addition to mccafe locations the company operates dessert centers at dessert centers customers can purchase a range of dessert items including the mcflurry and softserve ice cream it has approximately  dessert centers in the territoriesthe companys menus feature over three tiers of products entrylevel options such as its big pleasures small prices offerings and almuerzos colombianos colombian lunches in colombia core menu options such as the big mac happy meal and quarter pounder and premium options such as big tasty or angus premium hamburgers and chicken sandwiches and lowcalorie or lowsodium products that are marketed through common platforms rather than as individual items these platforms can be based on the type of products such as beef chicken salads or desserts or on the type of customer targeted such as the childrens menu it also offers new menu with fewer calories and less sugar and sodium in the majority of its territories it offers dairy products fresh fruits or vegetables with its happy meals in all of the territories except venezuelathe company competes with burger king yum brands carls junior subway habibs and bobs » full overview of arcon company address arcos dorados holdings inc wtc free zone drluis bonavita montevideo      p f  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation woods staton  sergio alonso  mariano tannenbaum  rogerio barreira  luis raganato  » more officers  directors arcos dorados holdings inc news briefarcos dorados q earnings per share  may   briefarcos dorados prices private placement of its  pct senior notes due  mar   briefarcos dorados announces commencement of tender offer mar   briefarcos dorados holdings q eps  mar   » more arcon news related topics stocksstock screenerrestaurants  bars arconmexico stock quote  arcos dorados holdings inc  bloomberg markets error could not add to watchlist x  watchlist arcos dorados holdings inc arconmm mexico price not available for arconmm mxn volume  previous close  before its here its on the bloomberg terminal learn more volume  previous close  current pe ratio ttm  earnings per share usd ttm  market cap b mxn  shares outstanding m  pricesales ttm  dividend indicated gross yield  sector consumer discretionary  price change  industry consumer services  price change  related videos there are currently no related videos for this ticker please check back later company news press releases there are currently no news stories for this ticker please check back later there are currently no press releases for this ticker please check back later profile arcos dorados holdings inc is a franchisee for an american fastfood burger restaurant the company has the right to own operate and grant franchises of restaurants in south and central america and the caribbean address dr luis bonavita  officewtc free zonemonte video uruguay phone  website wwwarcosdoradoscom executives board members woods w staton chairman sergio alonso chief executive officer mariano tannenbaum chief financial officer marcelo rabach chief operating o