rds the company has check points throughout the supply chain to ensure food safety cleanliness and consistency based on globally recognized established industry standards including the international organization for standardization iso the british retail consortium brc and the hazard analysis critical control plan haccp reducing consumptionedit mcdonald’s restaurants use a significant amount of energy specifically in cold storage to protect food safety during the past several years arcos dorados implemented a restaurant maintenance strategy to reduce water consumption energy utilization where possible and waste reduction at its restaurants as one example the company developed a collection and storage system for the water generated through condensation from the air conditioning equipment they used the collected water to clean external areas and to water plants reducing daily water consumption at one restaurant in brazil from  liters to  liters referencesedit  a b arcos dorados holdings reports fourthquarter and fullyear fiscal  results with record annual revenues eps operating margin and new bookings pdf arcos dorados holdings inc retrieved november   check date values in accessdate help  number of company employees   a b company description in homepage   a b c the companys description in reuters   arcos dorados plays pivotal role in  fifa world cup™ preparations yahoo finance  retrieved    a b c d e arcos dorados holdings inc  f  for  sec info retrieved    chairman and ceo of arcos dorados woods staton  latin trade group latintradecom  retrieved    patton leslie  mcdonald’s operator arcos dorados soars after initial offer bloomberg retrieved    latin america news latinvex retrieved    is arcos dorados a better pick than mcdonalds betafoolcom retrieved    a b arcos dorados reports fourth quarter  full year  financial results  business wire businesswirecom retrieved    a b arcos dorados holdings inc form b received   nasdaqcom retrieved    mcdonalds latin america   fl